{"tid":1866490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世!!] IG: starbuyhk 呃口罩錢！大家小心！幫推呀！！","createTime":"2020-02-06T18:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T11:59:23.000Z","uid":297939,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"385b815da871cc4de71cf7e68d6fcc8941fda92b","tid":1866490,"uid":297939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:29:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的，家下口罩咁缺，喺買唔到口罩情況下上網突然見到有ig shop賣一款3M口罩，聲稱可防菌重洗用。我見成99蚊一個，仲要係3M，店主仲要話可以防菌，心諗都同市面上嘅黑色可重用口罩有分別，咁就買咗2包。我喺ig shop: starbuyhk買。見佢follower有1.2萬，以往又有post開相sell野，心諗都唔會呃人掛，但原來真係冇得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有幾多follower好以前有幾多post都好都係會呃人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oiTy6z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oiTy6z.png&h=8e548b42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r269RTh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr269RTh.png&h=7d658836&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22jC0MF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22jC0MF.png&h=20ad323e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OFrFd6L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOFrFd6L.png&h=2fffb780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢叫我去旺角個大廈自取，買完翻到屋企睇個包裝，全部韓文，咁我就上網查字典。<br />\n<br />\n藍色口罩嘅包裝上只寫住100%純棉。黑色口罩嘅包裝上只寫住吸汗功能嘅材質。完全冇店主所講嘅防菌功能！<br />\n<br />\n我之後就wts揾店主講，問佢係咪比錯咗我。一早頭堅持話有，到我話我查完字典見到冇寫防菌，佢先影相佢手頭上嘅口罩話有，但佢手頭上嘅包裝根本就唔同我包裝！我send翻我取到口罩嘅相比佢，佢就話我開過冇得退，但我冇開過，我只係睇到包裝冇寫防菌！佢就block左我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實對話入面前前後後都block左幾次！<br />\n<br />\n所以大家要小心唔好再比佢呃！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68Rh0Re.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68Rh0Re.png&h=b0467b7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PKBYLhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPKBYLhW.png&h=b619add0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pA3bXX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pA3bXX.png&h=8a4d9312&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1HYPRX0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HYPRX0.png&h=d1be001d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CX40ebm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCX40ebm.png&h=77821feb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHC87wu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHC87wu.png&h=e8da78b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Y3XgpR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Y3XgpR.png&h=4be22b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTmYLie.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTmYLie.png&h=0128ad2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9GU24X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9GU24X.png&h=c5bee3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EL6t7wF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEL6t7wF.png&h=8efe43a8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GydXgqd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGydXgqd.png&h=585d9a53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Beaq9Lf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBeaq9Lf.png&h=adb7bb5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇高人可以指點下我點追究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我唔在乎冇咗嗰200蚊<br />\n係條氣唔順 依家災情咁嚴重都仲要賣口罩呃人<br />\n呢啲人唔死都冇用 有得吿我唔介意花時間 要我比錢去吿我都好樂意奉陪 我個人就係咁記仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763f7fb292dbdd6009924beb3fffd33b1db85c16","tid":1866490,"uid":297939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:33:17.000Z","ms